      <title>英国福利削减了汽车制造商的电动汽车野心的意外风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/uk-welfare-cuts-pose-unexpected-risk-to-carmakers-ev-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[将英国福利支出减少数十亿英镑的计划可能会产生意外的后果：破坏该国推动零排放车辆销售的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/uk-welfare-cuts-pose-unexpected-risk-to-carmakers-ev-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，在“控制”中遏制乌克兰战争的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/trump-says-efforts-to-contain-war-in-ukraine-under-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，阻止俄罗斯和乌克兰之间的战争进一步升级的努力是“控制的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/trump-says-efforts-to-contain-war-in-ukraine-under-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 04:25:51 GMT</pubDate>
